_sText:
A whole new designed sauna map by me. I made this map for christmas. In the T spawn is three buttons, each of them has a christmas music. 1 finnish song and 2 english. Under the map is large cold tunnel which leads to Ct and T base and to the showers and outside of the house. 

I tried to make the feeling of sauna as warm as possible. And the tunnel as cold as possible. Also the christmas night theme is very nice.

This is my first map after a six month break.
So don't be too cruel with the critisism :)

And sorry bad english!

EDIT: I forgot the picture of the tunnel, but you can test it by downloading the map :)
